{{Top|leg}}
The '''Centralia Memorial Spaceport''' was one of the oldest [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Seldom used, it was often the landing and embarking site for many [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and before, for their dangerous and private missions, when they couldn't land at the nearby [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].

Like many of the older spaceports of Coruscant, there was a move to make the CMS a monument, but many parties stopped it, although numerous other spaceports did in fact become monuments.

